Label: Time
Description: Abstract measure covering the concept of time

Label: Reponse Time
Description: A period of time taken to respond to a request

Label: Ambulance Response Time
Description: The period of time taken from request to arrival of an ambulance

Label: Non-emergency Police Response Time
Description: The period of time taken from request to arrival of police for a non-emergency

Label: Wait Time
Description: A period of time queued for service

Label: Hold Time
Description: The period of time queued to speak to an agent on the telephone
